title: Doorman/Spacious One Bedroom/Elevator/Laundry in Building
posting_body: ['This unit Is a large, beautiful one bedroom with fantastic finishes and', 'newly renovated appliances!', 'This unit has great storage space, an open concept kitchen complete with stainless steel appliances including a dishwasher and built-in cook microwave.', 'This unit has grand double paned windows – which allow tons of light and little noise in!', 'There are marble tile in the bathroom and hardwood floors through the units.', 'The rich dark toned and contrasting gorgeous white countertops pop the space for a modern feel.', 'This building is a prewar building, which features a live-in superintendent,', 'full-time doorman, elevators, Verizon Fios and laundry facilities.', 'Located within steps of Grand Central Station, the easiest transportation center within Manhattan: the subway lines running to and from Grand Central could easily position a rider nearly anywhere', 'in the City and beyond!', 'Brokers fee apply.', 'Serious inquiries only!', 'Must make 40x income & have', 'an excellent (700+) credit score in order to qualify!', 'Guarantors are welcome!']
